35:34.160 --> 35:36.080
Going home, Jack.

35:36.080 --> 35:37.520
I spoke to Roecklin in the lab,

35:37.520 --> 35:39.720
it won't be that long
before you get the results.

35:39.720 --> 35:42.360
My wife's going to meet me
in the lobby in 15 minutes.

35:42.360 --> 35:45.480
