35:45.480 --> 35:48.440
Hi, Pete.

35:48.440 --> 35:50.560
Boy, he's doing great.

35:50.560 --> 35:54.160
I thought it'd really screw him up
to go on his bottle this early,

35:54.160 --> 35:57.120
but he's had no trouble adjusting.

35:57.120 --> 36:00.680
They're more flexible
at that age, not like us.

36:00.680 --> 36:03.120
How you doing?

36:03.120 --> 36:05.760
Ah, you know.

36:05.760 --> 36:08.320
Lousy one day, miserable the next.

36:08.320 --> 36:12.320
It has to be tough
on the first holiday.

36:12.480 --> 36:16.320
It's funny, after Nina died...

36:16.320 --> 36:19.720
