Happy Thanksgiving.

38:54.240 --> 38:55.800
Happy Thanksgiving.

38:55.800 --> 38:59.080
Joe's going to be all right.

38:59.080 --> 39:01.000
Thank you.

39:01.000 --> 39:03.400
We found out what's
been making Joe sick.

39:03.400 --> 39:04.040
Well, what is it?

39:04.040 --> 39:05.200
Well, what is it?

39:05.200 --> 39:07.400
