have to miss a few weeks of school.

39:16.080 --> 39:17.680
You think you can cope with that?

39:17.680 --> 39:19.080
I'll try.

39:19.080 --> 39:21.720
First thing tomorrow morning
we have to get some food

39:21.720 --> 39:23.600
into that body of yours.

39:23.600 --> 39:26.280
I don't feel very hungry.

39:26.280 --> 39:29.960
We have some medication, it'll
help you get your appetite back.

39:29.960 --> 39:31.520
And if you cooperate,

39:31.520 --> 39:34.520
I may be able to work
a little miracle of my own.

39:34.520 --> 39:36.760
What do I have to do?

39:36.760 --> 39:39.680
Take the medicine,
and then concentrate.

39:39.680 --> 39:41.360
On what?

39:41.360 --> 39:45.360
That part of the turkey
you like best.

39:50.000 --> 39:54.000
Thank you, Doctor.

40:56.320 --> 40:58.600
Why didn't we have
this thing catered?

40:58.600 --> 41:01.600
At this point I'd just as soon
get some fast food and eat in bed.

41:01.600 --> 41:02.840
Come home with me -

41:02.840 --> 41:06.840
they just opened a new
Gobble To Go in my neighbourhood.

41:07.960 --> 41:09.200
Phew!

41:09.200 --> 41:10.840
You know, this makes a lot of sense -

41:10.840 --> 41:14.080
work 12 hours a day as a doctor,
I get off and moonlight as a busboy.

41:14.080 --> 41:16.040
Part of a new career
aptitude programme.

41:16.040 --> 41:18.920
In a few hours you can test your
skills loading the dishwasher.

41:18.920 --> 41:20.720
Oh, no, I forgot about cleaning up.

41:20.720 --> 41:21.920
Why couldn't we use
plastic silverware?

41:21.920 --> 41:23.200
